# Instalação Customizada

1) Selecionar "Minimal Install"

2) Seguir a instalação normal e reiniciar

2.5) max_parallel_downloads=10 to /etc/dnf/dnf.conf

3) sudo dnf install @base-x gnome-shell gnome-terminal nautilus firefox

4) sudo systemctl set-default graphical.target

5) reboot

6) sudo dnf install gnome-terminal-nautilus xdg-user-dirs xgd-user-dirs-gtk ffmpgegthumbnailer gnome-calculator gnome-system-monitor

7) sudo dnf install $(tr '\n' ' ' < pkgs)

8) https://docs.fedoraproject.org/en-US/quick-docs/setup_rpmfusion/

9) https://docs.fedoraproject.org/en-US/quick-docs/assembly_installing-plugins-for-playing-movies-and-music/

10) Instalar os pacotes extras (extra_pkgs)

11) https://docs.fedoraproject.org/en-US/quick-docs/how-to-set-nvidia-as-primary-gpu-on-optimus-based-laptops/

12) cargo install $(tr '\n' ' ' < cargo_pkgs)

13) https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim

14) https://github.com/neoclide/coc.nvim

15) https://rust-analyzer.github.io/manual.html#vimneovim

16) Configurar o firefox (bookmarks + addons)

17) Configurar o ckb-next

# Extras 

-> https://sourceforge.net/projects/hplip/files/hplip/3.21.6/hplip-3.21.6.run/download?use_mirror=nchc

-> sudo dnf install lutris

-> sudo dnf install steam
